{"tid":2235062,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［期待#love#］聽日立法會選內務同財委會主席，又可以睇牙泰做自己嘢了#good##good##yup#","createTime":"2020-10-08T11:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T03:15:20.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6eaecbd81b7d550af17a3c3b9857a56a556300fd","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻🤟🏻<br />\n<blockquote>   立法會內務委員會和財務委員會會議<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代立法會秘書處發出：<br />\n　　立法會內務委員會明日（十月九日）下午二時三十分在立法會綜合大樓（綜合大樓）會議室1舉行會議，選舉二○二○至二○二一年度會期內務委員會主席及副主席。<br />\n　　此外，立法會財務委員會將緊接內務委員會會議後，在綜合大樓會議室1舉行會議，選舉二○二○至二○二一年度會期財務委員會主席及副主席。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年10月8日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間16時10分<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b132ec1e8022fd9a8e5e149f1ff4df67b376f86f","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人有之前白兵嗰張「聽日內會打硬」張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7679e9f6cd8d57b37b0400ae6422788e462498","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:16:28.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰憂慮《国安法》下終審法院判決亦可被推翻<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192649</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n国安法：無需陪審團 <br />\n熱狗：挽回司法公正，建議區院引入陪審團<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2096511\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2096511</a><br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊：鄭松泰說他完全不相信數據保安，不知道他是否因此而沒膽量參加初選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2172024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2172024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰談產假延長：我害怕回家被妻子責問，所以我不會投反對票，妥協投棄權票。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2171943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2171943</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰不點名針對有區議員躲在天橋協助警察捉拿非法賽車<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2115237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2115237</a><br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰談国歌法：我曾在北京生活5年，博士學位在北大取得，論黨的語言比謝偉俊更熟悉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fHCspS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fHCspS</a><br />\n<br />\n[又爭] 鄭松泰：本黨是第一個政黨在瘟疫初期在街頭派發口罩，並開街站呼籲大眾勤洗手，注意衛生。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2143683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2143683</a>"},{"pid":"e7fc69df75d879236c165cfa92b678803bcb1afd","tid":2235062,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fa0d30e086634c0ba846097f7f0a984dd3ecf10","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7fc69df75d879236c165cfa92b678803bcb1afd","tid":2235062,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b132ec1e8022fd9a8e5e149f1ff4df67b376f86f","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人有之前白兵嗰張「聽日內會打硬」張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6de8a1d84a7cfc44fca88395638567b1987c00","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T12:26:41.000Z","msg":"波台好多熱血公民成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冷處理樓主"},{"pid":"03da19ce46a9d1b40e84b9be8dc587a72c8afdd6","tid":2235062,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe720a002e0c66dd71f9d384e3b3ce0da4e9603f"